name: Tenable: assets that have the Tenable agent installed
Tenable: assets that haven't been scanned by Tenable in over 2 weeks
Tenable: no authenticated scan has been run in the last 30 days
Tenable: authenticated scan never occurred or is older than 30 days
Tenable: Tenable fingerprint more generic than runZero fingerprint for Linux assets
Tenable: Generic Tenable fingerprint for Windows OS identification
Tenable: assets with over an 8 ACR (asset criticality rating) score
Tenable: High and Critical severity vulnerabilities that are on CISA's KEV
query: source:tenable AND (plugin.xrefs.type:"CISA-KNOWN-EXPLOITED" OR kev:cisa) AND (severity:high OR severity:critical)

name: Tenable: newly reported critical vulns listed on the KEV
description: Critical vulnerabilities are to be remediated within 15 days per CISA guidance.
query: source:tenable AND (plugin.xrefs.type:"CISA-KNOWN-EXPLOITED" OR kev:cisa) AND severity:critical AND firstFoundTS:<24hours

name: Tenable: newly reported high severity vulns listed on the KEV
description: High severity vulnerabilities are to be remediated within 30 days per CISA guidance.
query: source:tenable AND (plugin.xrefs.type:"CISA-KNOWN-EXPLOITED" OR kev:cisa) AND severity:high AND firstFoundTS:<24hours

name: Tenable: newly reported KEV vulns with 6 months to remediate per BOD 22-01
query: source:tenable AND (plugin.xrefs.type:"CISA-KNOWN-EXPLOITED" OR kev:cisa) AND firstFoundTS:<24hours

name: Tenable: critical severity vulnerabilities with public exploits
query: source:tenable AND plugin.exploitabilityEase:"Exploits are available" AND severity:critical

name: Tenable: high and critical severity vulnerabilities where exploits are not required
query: source:tenable AND plugin.exploitabilityEase:"No exploit is required" AND (severity:critical OR severity:high)

name: Tenable: vulnerabilities with an available patch
